text: Leech Lake is an unincorporated community in Leech Lake Township, Cass County, Minnesota, United States. It is along State Highway 371 (MN 371) near 100th Street NW, Cass County Road 62. Nearby places include Walker, Laporte, and Steamboat Bay of Leech Lake. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Cass County, Minnesota Category:Unincorporated communities in Minnesota
title: Leech Lake, Minnesota
